      <title>主题透明化</title>
      <link href="/2022/06/15/hello-world/"/>
      <url>/2022/06/15/hello-world/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>在配置butterfly主题时，一直想尝试如何更改主题界面的透明化，进而有了这篇博客。</p><h2 id="主界面透明化">主界面透明化</h2><p>在主题配置文件内</p><blockquote><p>.yml</p></blockquote><h3 id="页脚背景调整">页脚背景调整</h3><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">footer_bg:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>页脚背景需要调为false</p><h3 id="消除页脚">消除页脚</h3><p>在将页脚背景调为false后，可以看到页脚为纯色背景</p><p>找到文件 footer.styl（以下为我的目录)</p><blockquote><p>E:\Blog\themes\butterfly\source\css_layout\footer.styl</p></blockquote><p>有如下代码</p><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">background</span>: $light-blue</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>将其注释掉，即可消掉页脚。</p><h3 id="实现主界面透明">实现主界面透明</h3><p>在主题配置文件下</p><blockquote><p>.yml</p></blockquote><p>找到主页上方图像和背景图像</p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">index_img:</span> <span class="string">/img/top/27.jpg</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">background:</span> <span class="string">url(/img/top/27.jpg)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>注意背景图像的配置格式</p><p>最后，主界面的透明化就实现啦！</p><p>实际效果: <a href="http://hlp-shark.top/">我的博客</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
